commit message: Update URL for downloading the binaries for integration-android as well.
Re-enable fetching of exchange rates on Heartbleed vulnerable devices.
Change wording to backup/restore wallet, rather than private keys.
Use Guava's Base64 implementaton for encrypting wallet backups.
Fix prefix used in pending coins message.
Filter exchange rates by a search query.
Get rid of the Android application record for NFC NDEF messages.
Add coin loss warnings to the wallet restore dialogs.
